## CODE STYLE
- Functional components only, no class components
- Named exports for components, default exports for pages
- Interfaces over types for object shapes
- Early returns over nested conditionals
- Descriptive variable names — no single letters except 
  loop indices
- Group imports: React first, then external, then internal

## WHEN IN DOUBT
Build the simplest thing that works first.
Ship it.
Improve it after.
The terminal being live and functional is always more 
important than it being perfect.
